42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Oscillating_Fan\" title=\"Oscillating Fan\"><img alt=\"Oscillating Fan.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Oscillating_Fan.png?eab1aa\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/64px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Electrical_Doodad\" title=\"Electrical Doodad\"><img alt=\"Electrical Doodad.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Electrical_Doodad.png?d7bfec\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Alloy\" title=\"Alloy\"><img alt=\"Alloy.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Alloy.png?15755a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lantern\" title=\"Lantern\"><img alt=\"Lantern.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Lantern.png?dc0f6a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Key_to_the_City\" title=\"Key to the City\"><img alt=\"Key to the City.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Key_to_the_City.png/42px-Key_to_the_City.png?775850\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lamp_Post\" title=\"Lamp Post\"><img alt=\"Lamp Post.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Lamp_Post.png?9c8661\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/64px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Electrical Doodads were first introduced in the <i>Reign of Giants</i> DLC. During the Early Access phase of the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Hamlet\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Hamlet\">Hamlet</a></i> DLC, they were then retroactively added to the base game to allow Wagstaff to craft his specific items.</li>\n<li>Electrical Doodads used to be crafted from the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Refine_Tab\" title=\"Refine Tab\">Refine Tab</a>.</li>\n<li>Electrical Doodads were initially added to make it harder to craft crucial objects, like the Alchemy Engine.</li>\n<li>Per Wagstaff&#x27;s quote as well as its appearance, the Electrical Doodad is a diode despite its spawn code referring to it as a transistor.</li></ul>\n<div></div>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"DST-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Electrical_Doodad#DST-0\">DST</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"DS-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Electrical_Doodad#DS-0\">DS</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"RoG-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Electrical_Doodad#RoG-0\">RoG</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"SW-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Electrical_Doodad#SW-0\">SW</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Ham-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Electrical_Doodad#Ham-0\">Ham</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n <p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
